euporia.tecnling.retoricaweb.dsl.dsltest

Interface DslTestListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DslTestBaseListener, DslTestImplListener

    public interface DslTestListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by DslTestParser.
